counts <- read.csv("GSE89225_Illumina_counts.csv", row.names=1)

mart <- read.table("human_mart.txt", sep="\t", header=1, check.names = F)

1: 

dds <- DESeqDataSetFromMatrix(countData = counts,
                              colData = conditions,
                              design = ~ tissue + cells) #  DeseqDataSet 

max_8000 <- names(rev(sort(rowSums(counts(dds))))[1:8000]) #  8000   
dds_new <- dds[rownames(dds) %in% max_8000,] #    8000   
dds_log <- rlog(dds_new) #   
dds_cor <- cor(assay(dds_log)) #      cor (    mm,  m   )
dds_nes <- 1 - dds_cor #    1 - cor
dds_dist <- dist(dds_nes) #    

dds_clust_1 <- hclust(dds_dist, method="average") # ,     : average
dds_clust_2 <- hclust(dds_dist, method="complete") # ,     : complete
dds_clust_3 <- hclust(dds_dist, method="single") # ,     : single

plot_1 <- plot(dds_clust_1)

plot_2 <- plot(dds_clust_2)

plot_3 <- plot(dds_clust_3)

2: K-means

counts <- counts[,names(counts) != "treg_NBP_patient3"] #  
conditions <- conditions[row.names(conditions) != "treg_NBP_patient3", ] #  

dds_wo_out <- DESeqDataSetFromMatrix(countData = counts,
                              colData = conditions,
                              design = ~ tissue + cells) #  DeseqDataSet 

max_8000_wo <- names(rev(sort(rowSums(counts(dds_wo_out))))[1:8000]) #  8000   

dds_new_wo <- dds_wo_out[rownames(dds_wo_out) %in% max_8000_wo,] #    8000   

dds_log_wo <- rlog(dds_new_wo) #   

clustering <- Kmeans(assay(dds_log_wo), 6, method="correlation", iter.max=20000) #   Kmeans   amap   correlation, c    6      20000
head(clustering$cluster)
## ENSG00000000003 ENSG00000000419 ENSG00000000457 ENSG00000000460 ENSG00000000971 ENSG00000001036 
##               2               3               6               1               5               1

Heatmap

# conditions[, 1] # 
# conditions[, 2] # 

dds_log_wo_a <- assay(dds_log_wo)
sort_clust <- sort(clustering$cluster)
to_visualise <- dds_log_wo_a[names(sort_clust),
                            order(conditions[, 2],conditions[, 1])] 

to_visualise <- t(apply(to_visualise, 1, function(r) {
  (r - min(r)) / (max(r) - min(r))
}))

m <- as.data.frame(sort_clust)
m$sort_clust <- as.factor(m$sort_clust)


pheatmap(to_visualise, 
         show_rownames =F, cluster_rows = F,
         cluster_cols=F,
         annotation_col = conditions, annotation_row = m)
